[var(--color-cream)] mb-4 opacity-0 translate-y-3 animate-slide-up [animation-delay:320ms]\">The gallery<br/><em class=\"font-sub italic text-[var(--color-ochre)]\">extends</em><br/>beyond the walls.</h1></div></section><section class=\"px-6 md:px-12 py-20 bg-[var(--color-parchment)]\"><div class=\"reveal\"><div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[var(--color-sienna)] mb-12 flex items-center gap-4 before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] before:block before:w-8 before:h-[1px] before:bg-[var(--color-sienna)]\">Studio 201 Coffee</div></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-[clamp(2rem,3.5vw,2.8rem)] font-light leading-[1.1] max-w-[600px] mb-8 mt-12 text-[var(--color-near-black)]\">The café has always been the other room of the gallery.</h2></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d2\"><p class=\"font-body text-[14px] leading-[1.85] text-[var(--color-warm-slate)] max-w-[580px]\">A place where the conversation continues after the last painting. Where ideas settle alongside espresso. Where the work of the gallery — its pace, its attention, its quiet — extends into the rhythm of daily life.</p></div></section><section class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 bg-[var(--color-parchment)] border-t border-[var(--color-rule)]\"><div class=\"reveal reveal-d1\"><div class=\"h-[50vw] md:h-full min-h-[50vh] bg-gradient-to-br from-[#5a4838] to-[#4a3828] overflow-hidden\"></div></div><div class=\"px-6 md:px-[64px] py-16 md:py-[80px] flex flex-col justify-center border-t md:border-t-0 md:border-l border-[var(--color-rule)]\"><div class=\"reveal\"><p class=\"font-mono text-[9px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[var(--color-warm-slate)] mb-6\">This Season</p></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d1\"><p class=\"font-body text-[13px] leading-[1.85] text-[var(--color-warm-slate)] mb-6\">This season, we&#x27;re serving a natural process Ethiopian through the Hario — bright, fruit-forward, good for slow mornings. The filter menu changes monthly alongside the gallery program.</p></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d2\"><blockquote class=\"font-sub text-[clamp(1.3rem,2.5vw,1.9rem)] font-light italic leading-[1.4] text-[var(--color-near-black)] border-l-2 border-[var(--color-sienna)] pl-7 my-12\">&quot;The café slows you down in the best possible way. You come for fifteen minutes. You stay for two hours.&quot;<footer class=\"not-italic font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-[var(--color-warm-slate)] block mt-4\">— A Regular</footer></blockquote></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d3\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5 font-body text-[14px] text-[var(--color-near-black)]\"><span><strong>Tuesday — Saturday</strong>   9:00 — 18:00</span><span><strong>Sunday</strong>   10:00 — 16:00</span><span class=\"text-[var(--color-warm-slate)]\">No reservations. Come as you are.</span></div></div></div></section><section class=\"px-6 md:px-12 py-20 md:py-30 bg-[var(--color-linen)] border-t border-[var(--color-rule)]\"><div class=\"reveal\"><div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[var(--color-sienna)] mb-12 flex items-center gap-4 before:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] before:block before:w-8 before:h-[1px] before:bg-[var(--color-sienna)]\">Pop-ups &amp; Residencies</div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-start mt-16\"><div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d1\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-[clamp(2rem,3.5vw,2.8rem)] font-light leading-[1.1] mb-6 text-[var(--color-near-black)]\">Temporary homes for urgent ideas.</h2><p class=\"font-body text-[13px] leading-[1.85] text-[var(--color-warm-slate)] mb-8\">Studio 201 hosts short-term residencies and pop-up programs for artists, publishers, and cultural practitioners who need a room of their own. Each residency leaves something behind — in the archive, in the walls, in the conversation.</p></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d2\"><div class=\"border border-[var(--color-rule)] p-8 mt-4 bg-[var(--color-parchment)]\"><p class=\"font-mono text-[9px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[var(--color-warm-slate)] mb-3\">Currently in Residence</p><h3 class=\"font-display text-[1.3rem] font-light mb-2 text-[var(--color-near-black)]\">Tao Printshop</h3><p class=\"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--color-sienna)] mb-4\">3 Feb — 28 Mar 2026</p><p class=\"font-body text-[12px] leading-[1.75] text-[var(--color-warm-slate)]\">A risograph studio operating in the gallery&#x27;s back room — printing editions, hosting workshops, and making the process visible.</p></div></div></div><div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d3\"><p class=\"font-mono text-[9px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[var(--color-warm-slate)] mb-6\">Past Residencies</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><div class=\"reveal reveal-d4\"><div class=\"py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-rule)] flex justify-between items-center group cursor-none\"><span class=\"font-display text-[1.1rem] font-light transition-colors group-hover:text-[var(--color-sienna)]\">Blank Canvas Studio</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[var(--color-warm-slate)]\">Apparel / 2025</span></div></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d5\"><div class=\"py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-rule)] flex justify-between items-center group cursor-none\"><span class=\"font-display text-[1.1rem] font-light transition-colors group-hover:text-[var(--color-sienna)]\">Kanto Reading Room</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[var(--color-warm-slate)]\">Library / 2024</span></div></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d5\"><div class=\"py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-rule)] flex justify-between items-center group cursor-none\"><span class=\"font-display text-[1.1rem] font-light transition-colors group-hover:text-[var(--color-sienna)]\">Materia Ceramics</span><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[var(--color-warm-slate)]\">Objects / 2024</span></div></div><div class=\"reveal reveal-d5\"><div class=\"py-4 flex just